        <item>
            <title>0.3.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 09:08:24 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>3002</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Layered AI provider architecture: Apple Foundation Models, MLX, Ollama developer mode, and rule-based fallback</li>
<li>Ask DiskWise chat with autocomplete and dynamic suggested questions when Apple Intelligence is available</li>
<li>AI executive summary in Storage Intelligence after each scan</li>
<li>AI assistant settings for provider preference and Ollama developer mode</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Improvements</strong><ul>
<li>DMG installer windows always show the Finder status bar when opened</li>
<li>Saved scan prompt after startup when cached scan data is available</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Fixes</strong><ul>
<li>DMG status bar configuration no longer fails during release packaging</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
